	Fix ordinalSuffix for negative arguments (issue #20).

	string_ext.lua: use Lua terminology "pattern" rather than "regex"

2013-02-22  Gary V. Vaughan  <gary@gnu.org>

	specs: add specl specification for string_ext module.
